    "Recently, the emergence of AIGC has provided new solutions to these challenges.",
    "Different from traditional AI, AIGC focuses on creating new content and generating solutions, which provides greater creativity and flexibility.",
    "By performing in-depth data analysis, it can generate innovative solutions based on existing information, providing diverse strategies for traffic management.",
    "On one hand, by integrating various technologies such as generative AI algorithms, natural language processing (NLP), and computer vision, AIGC holds significant potential to enhance human-computer interaction in traffic scenarios.",
    "Such applications mainly exist in three major areas: dialog and reasoning, prediction and decision-making, and multimodal generation."
